{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311782, "create_time": 1658716051, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "能，同一个CPU上，Windows和Linux双系统，macOS和Windows双系统，都是常规操作", "timestamp": 1658716051}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311783, "create_time": 1658716057, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "那自然是可以的", "timestamp": 1658716057}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311785, "create_time": 1658716121, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "软件对芯片的适配，关键是指令集（ARM/x64/risc-v这些）而不是芯片厂商或型号", "timestamp": 1658716121}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311787, "create_time": 1658716218, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "如果你要做一个新的指令集的话，你可以选择在运行时翻译，这样效率较低，如果追求效率的话你需要做一套新的编译器、汇编器，然后把所有软件重新编译", "timestamp": 1658716218}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 311799, "create_time": 1658716889, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 了解了！那如果一个原本主做Android的芯片厂商希望去适配鸿蒙系统，需要另外进行开发吗？还是只改下固件之类的就可以呢？", "timestamp": 1658716889}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 312062, "create_time": 1658728256, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "是你的操作系统去适配芯片，你的安卓芯片厂商用的是ARMv7 v8的指令集，就找基于ARMv7 v8的指令集的鸿蒙操作系统，就能用", "timestamp": 1658728256}], "create_time": 1658715995, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1658728256, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 6, "pid": 88202, "poll": null, "reply": 6, "text": "请问：同一块芯片能用在不同的操作系统上吗？或者说，为了适配一个新的操作系统，需要对芯片进行怎样的调整呢？", "timestamp": 1658715995}}